Label: Incomplete Not Resolved Fail
Definition: Failing/no pass/unsatisfactory grade awarded because incomplete not resolved satisfactorily

Label: In Progress
Definition: Current enrollment course in progress, permanent grade not yet assigned

Label: Not Yet Reported
Definition: No grade reported yet by instructor (although the course has ended)

Label: Other Fail
Definition: Other not passing/unsatisfactory grade not described above

Label: Other Pass
Definition: Other passing/satisfactory grade not described above

Label: Pass Fail Fail
Definition: Failing grade in a course (credit or non-credit) which is normally, or based on student option, given a pass/fail or satisfactory/unsatisfactory designation

Label: Pass Fail Pass
Definition: Passing grade in a course (credit or non-credit) which is normally, or based on student option, given a pass/fail or satisfactory/unsatisfactory designation

Label: Transfer No Grade
Definition: Transfer credit; grade not carried on receiving institution's transcript

Label: Withdrew No Penalty
Definition: Withdrew without penalty or pass/fail designation

Label: Grade Status Codes
Definition: Special enrollment or completion status of this course
